* ONNX Runtime
  The semantic layer links the ONNX Runtime native library. When building
  the `onnx` feature, it is downloaded at build time by the `ort` crate.
  ONNX Runtime is distributed under the MIT License.
  https://github.com/microsoft/onnxruntime

* Embedding model: paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2
  The semantic layer requires a local embedding model. It is downloaded at
  install time from the Hugging Face Hub (it is NOT part of this repository
  or the release archives). The model is published by sentence-transformers
  under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  https://huggingface.co/sentence-transformers/paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2

